A private school in Matungulu, Machakos county, is donating water to residents from drought stricken areas.Kangundo Junior Group of School's director Charles Kilonzo said it provides 40,000 litres of weekly.He addressed the press at Kyaume Primary School in Tala yesterday after distributing water.He said women and children from Kyaume, Sengani and Katine sub-locations spend nights queuing for water at Kyamole Spring, 4 kilometres from their homes.